-- Disney Revises ‘Avengers’ Weekend Tally Up to $207.4 Million
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   P a l m e r i
-- 2012-05-07T19:22:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-07/disney-revises-avengers-weekend-tally-up-to-207-4-million.html
Walt Disney Co. (DIS)  said “Marvel’s The
Avengers” collected a record $207.4 million in weekend ticket
sales in the U.S. and Canada.  The revised total marked an increase from the $200.3
million reported initially and came in an e-mail today from the
Burbank, California-based company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Palmeri in Los Angeles at 
 cpalmeri1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
